OL,3,CBournemouth stroke patient campaigns
OL,4,Cfor better rehabilitation for others
OL,6,F"The rehabilitation that I received
OL,7,Fstarted very quickly after I had the
OL,8,Fstroke," David said.
OL,10,F"People called physiotherapists came
OL,11,Falong with the view of getting me home.
OL,13,F"Gradually I realised that there was a
OL,14,Ffuture to be had."
OL,16,FDavid is now fit enough to drive
OL,17,Fhimself to a local heart health group.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
