OL,3,CBournemouth stroke patient campaigns
OL,4,Cfor better rehabilitation for others
OL,6,FIn a statement a spokesperson said:
OL,7,F'We're rolling out specialist stroke
OL,8,Frehabilitation in people's homes, so
OL,9,Fmore people can get the right care
OL,10,Fwithout having to rely on hospital
OL,11,Fstays."
